# Module 3 - Conditions
## Level 1 - Challenge 3

Problem
Find the largest of two numbers.

Instructions
1. Ask the user to enter two numbers.
2. Compare both numbers.
3. Print the larger number.

Example Input
4
7

Example Output
7

Hint
Use if statement to compare two numbers.

Broken Code
a = int(input("Enter first number: "))
b = int(input("Enter second number: "))
if a > b
print(a)
else
print(b)

Correct Code
a = int(input("Enter first number: "))
b = int(input("Enter second number: "))
if a > b:
    print(a)
else:
    print(b)
